y|Pablo Picasso}}\n{{Wikiquote|Pablo Picasso|Picasso}}\n* {{Internet Archive author |sname=Pablo Picasso |sopt=t}}\n* {{worldcat id|id=lccn-n78-86005}}\n* {{Discogs artist|Pablo Picasso|Picasso}}\n* {{IMDb name|0681444|Picasso}}\n* {{FrenchSculptureCensus | 2=Picasso}}\n* [https://www.guggenheim.org/artwork/artist/pablo-picasso Picasso] at the [[Solomon R. Guggenheim Museum|Guggenheim Museum]]\n* [http://collections.lacma.org/node/166980 Picasso] at the [[Los Angeles County Museum of Art]] (LACMA)\n* [http://www.metmuseum.org/toah/hd/pica/hd_pica.htm Picasso] at [[Metropolitan Museum of Art]] (New York City, New York)\n* {{MoMA artist|4609|Picasso}} (MoMA) (New York City, New York)\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20050830044503/http://www.musee-picasso.fr/ Mus\u00e9e National Picasso] (Paris, France)\n* [http://www.museopicassomalaga.org Museo Picasso M\u00e1laga] (M\u00e1laga, Spain)\n* [http://www.museupicasso.bcn.es Museu Picasso] (Barcelona, Spain)\n* [http://www.nga.gov/content/ngaweb/Collection/artist-info.1783.html#works Picasso] at the [[National Gallery of Art]] (Washington, DC)\n* [http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k1073374c/f81.item Picasso, L'Esprit nouveau: revue internationale d'esth\u00e9tique, 1920]. Gallica, Biblioth\u00e8que nationale de France\n\n{{Pablo Picasso}}\n{{Modernism}}\n{{Cubism}}\n{{Authority control|MBA=}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Picasso, Pablo}}\n[[Category:Pablo Picasso| ]]\n[[Category:1881 births]]\n[[Category:1939 New York World's Fair artists]]\n[[Category:1973 deaths]]\n[[Category:19th-century Spanish painters]]\n[[Category:20th-century ceramists]]\n[[Category:20th-century sculptors]]\n[[Category:20th-century Spanish painters]]\n[[Category:Ballet designers]]\n[[Category:Burials in Provence-Alpes-C\u00f4te d'Azur]]\n[[Category:Child artists]]\n[[Category:Cubist artists]]\n[[Category:Directors of the Museo del Prado]]\n[[Category:Former Roman Catholics]]\n[[Category:French Communist Party members]]\n[[Category:Lenin Peace Prize recipie